EntityProcessor
protected class EntityProcessor.UnhandledObjectException
extends java.lang.RuntimeException

This exception gets thrown if an object turns out to be an unexpected type. This could occur with a VERTEX that can be both a 2 or 3 dimensional object. If the VERTEX is 2d no problem, but SVG does not handle 3D objects so we throw an exception.

1.6
